snippet.title: DodgeballDojo 1.0.0 Preview Video
snippet.description:
Big 2 Family Friend Card Game 

Play competitive card games inspired by Big 2 with friends and family! Collect cool anime and manga Spirit Pets, and watch Athletes dodge, duck, dip, dive, and dodge!
